#TrustGod 
Greater things take place when you trust God. Last Saturday's weather was the worst I'd seen in years with torrential rain, wind and flooding in Atlantic City. I prayed to God asking Him to adjust the weather conditions, but instead the weather conditions grew worse. I wondered if people would brave the weather to attend our 2nd Annual Greatness In You, Inc. Mother Daughter Tea. Not only did the girls, boys, women and men show up but we also had to put out additional tables & chairs. God proved himself once again that it doesn't matter what it looks like.. HE still has everything under control and in control. And I'm oh so grateful!  Thank you Lord! 🙌🏽
We are Greatness In You, Inc.!
